data.text:
SCHEDULE

THE SKY IS OUR STAGE

There is nothing like experiencing a Thunderbirds performance in person. Watch powerful fighter jets elegantly maneuver in the sky with only a few feet separating each wingtip. It’s a multisensory experience that will leave you impressed and inspired. While admission to air shows on military installations is generally free and open to the public, the cost to attend civilian air shows may vary. Please visit the individual shows’ sites for prices and more information.
